						<summary>

						<p>Records that the body <hi rend="italic">Munnūṟṟuvar</hi> of Nālukarai-nāḍu had agreed to protect Maṇgalam, a <hi rend="italic">dēvadāna</hi> village of Rājasēkara-Īsvaramuḍaiya-Mahādēva temple built by Koṅgilāṇḍār a resident of Mudalināyappaḷḷi <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Jayaṅgoṇḍasōḻapuram. This record was written by Bhaṭṭālagan Vīrakēsari <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Irumuḍi Iḍaṅgai uyyakkoṇḍān of Siṟuvūr in Kiḷiyūr nāḍu. </p>						

						</summary>
